          AI-powered document automation for contractors who want to spend less time on estimates and more time building.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Get Free Assessment
          </a>
          <a href="#use-cases" class="btn btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">
